Create a clear structure to organize documentation, code, and resources. Here’s a suggested layout:

superstacks-campaign-superchain/
├── docs/                     # Documentation about SuperStacks and Superchain
│   ├── overview.md           # Campaign overview
│   ├── participation-guide.md # How to participate
│   └── faq.md                # Frequently asked questions
├── contracts/                # Smart contract examples (e.g., SuperchainERC20)
│   ├── SuperchainERC20.sol   # Example contract for interoperable tokens
│   └── deploy.js             # Deployment script
├── frontend/                 # Optional frontend for interacting with campaign
│   ├── src/
│   └── package.json
├── scripts/                  # Utility scripts for automation
│   └── check-xp.js           # Example script to check XP leaderboard
├── README.md                 # Main repository README
├── LICENSE                   # License file (e.g., MIT)

